creator: Anonymous
description:
LibriVox recording of The Keepsake (version 2) by Anonymous.
Read in English by SamanthaBraswell; Jude; John Burlinson; Sonia; Diana Schmidt; Kathleen Moore
This is a cute little volume of poems for children. Listeners may wish to refer to the text to see the pretty illustrations. - Summary by Carolin
For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording.

For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org.
